metadata.name: Pistons RareAccess Legend
metadata.description:
As a Pistons RareAccess holder, you can use the team portal to redeem digital benefits, including access to behind-the-scenes footage, community polls, private Huddle Sessions with members of the Pistons organization plus exclusive discounts with official partners. 
As a Legend Access Pass holder you can enjoy access to premium benefits. 
View a full list of benefits: https://pistons.rareaccess.xyz/ 
Physical benefits, including memorabilia and game tickets, can only be claimed by the original wallet holder. 
Season 1 Passes are valid through July 31, 2023 
Terms and conditions apply: https://pistons.rareaccess.xyz/terms-and-conditions
